ivate cloud\",\n 70 |     accent: \"#00FF9D\"\n 71 |   },\n 72 |   {\n 73 |     id: \"factory\" as const,\n 74 |     label: \"GFF Factory\",\n 75 |     badge: \"Industrial Scale Fleets\",\n 76 |     desc: \"High-volume cognitive agent orchestration, automated pipelines, and enterprise-wide federated data mesh networks.\",\n 77 |     weeks: \"12 - 24 Weeks\",\n 78 |     squad: \"2 Architects, 4 Core Engineers, 1 QA Auditor, 1 Delivery Director\",\n 79 |     outcome: \"Multi-agent automated workforce operating across production databases\",\n 80 |     accent: \"#9D00FF\"\n 81 |   },\n 82 |   {\n 83 |     id: \"operate\" as const,\n 84 |     label: \"GFF Operate\",\n 85 |     badge: \"SLA-Driven Co-Run\",\n 86 |     desc: \"Continuous proactive monitoring, scheduled compliance updates, model weight updates, and guaranteed performance SLAs.\",\n 87 |     weeks: \"Ongoing Execution\",\n 88 |     squad: \"Dedicated Site Reliability Fleet, Lead AI Performance Engineer\",\n 89 |     outcome: \"Guaranteed 99.9% uptime, compliance reports, and proactive optimizations\",\n 90 |     accent: \"#E5A93C\"\n 91 |   }\n 92 | ];\n 93 | \n 94 | const BUDGET_RANGES = [\n 95 |   { id: \"tier-1\", label: \"Discovery Capital ($50K - $250K)\", desc: \"Suited for GFF Garage exploration and sandbox verification.\" },\n 96 |   { id: \"tier-2\", label: \"Strategic Platform ($250K - $1M)\", desc: \"Optimal for core GFF Foundry setup and VPC deployments.\" },\n 97 |   { id: \"tier-3\", label: \"Industrial Scale ($1M+)\", desc: \"Required for GFF Factory federated rollouts and persistent co-run.\" }\n 98 | ];\n 99 | \n100 | // ==========================================\n101 | // 2. Types & Interface\n102 | // ==========================================\n103 | \n104 | interface ProposalIntakeInputs {\n105 |   companyName: string;\n106 |   industry: Industry;\n107 |   companySize: CompanySize;\n108 |   primaryChallenge: string;\n109 |   customChallenge: string;\n110 |   priorityOutcomes: string[];\n111 |   targetTimeline: string;\n112 |   preferredEngagementPath: \"garage\" | \"foundry\" | \"factory\" | \"operate\";\n113 |   budgetRange: string;\n114 |   geography: string;\n115 |   stakeholders: string;\n116 | }\n117 | \n118 | const INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS: ProposalIntakeInputs = {\n119 |   companyName: \"\",\n120 |   industry: \"banking\",\n121 |   companySize: \"enterprise\",\n122 |   primaryChallenge: \"compliance-risk\",\n123 |   customChallenge: \"\",\n124 |   priorityOutcomes: [\"zero-retention\", \"sub-150ms-latency\"],\n125 |   targetTimeline: \"90-days\",\n126 |   preferredEngagementPath: \"foundry\",\n127 |   budgetRange: \"tier-2\",\n128 |   geography: \"\",\n129 |   stakeholders: \"\"\n130 | };\n131 | \n132 | const compilingMessages = [\n133 |   \"Spinning up local compiler sandbox...\",\n134 |   \"Querying GFF strategic taxonomy parameters...\",\n135 |   \"Applying regulatory compliance standards override...\",\n136 |   \"Sizing GFF delivery squad parameters...\",\n137 |   \"Configuring isolated virtual boundary rules...\",\n138 |   \"Enforcing strict zero-data retention pipelines...\",\n139 |   \"Generating premium SOW specifications...\"\n140 | ];\n141 | \n142 | export default function ProposalBuilderPage() {\n143 |   const [inputs, setInputs] = useState<ProposalIntakeInputs>(INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS);\n144 |   const [step, setStep] = useState<\"configure\" | \"compiling\" | \"preview\">(\"configure\");\n145 |   const [activeStepGate, setActiveStepGate] = useState<1 | 2 | 3>(1);\n146 |   const [compilingStepIndex, setCompilingStepIndex] = useState(0);\n147 |   const [copied, setCopied] = useState(false);\n148 |   const [saved, setSaved] = useState(false);\n149 |   const [hasSavedDraft, setHasSavedDraft] = useState(false);\n150 |   const [activePreviewSection, setActivePreviewSection] = useState<string>(\"executive-summary\");\n151 |   const [signName, setSignName] = useState(\"\");\n152 |   const [signTitle, setSignTitle] = useState(\"\");\n153 |   const [isSigned, setIsSigned] = useState(false);\n154 |   const [mounted, setMounted] = useState(false);\n155 |   const [validationErrors, setValidationErrors] = useState<Record<string, string>>({});\n156 | \n157 |   useEffect(() => {\n158 |     setMounted(true);\n159 |     if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n160 |       const draft = localStorage.getItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\");\n161 |       if (draft) setHasSavedDraft(true);\n162 |     }\n163 |   }, []);\n164 | \n165 |   const validateStep = (gate: 1 | 2 | 3): boolean => {\n166 |     const errors: Record<string, string> = {};\n167 |     if (gate === 1) {\n168 |       if (!inputs.industry) errors.industry = \"Please select a primary industry vertical.\";\n169 |       if (!inputs.companySize) errors.companySize = \"Please specify company scale.\";\n170 |     } else if (gate === 2) {\n171 |       if (!inputs.primaryChallenge) errors.primaryChallenge = \"Please identify your primary business challenge.\";\n172 |       if (inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && !inputs.customChallenge.trim()) {\n173 |         errors.customChallenge = \"Please specify your custom corporate obstacle.\";\n174 |       }\n175 |       if (inputs.priorityOutcomes.length === 0) {\n176 |         errors.priorityOutcomes = \"Please select at least one priority target outcome.\";\n177 |       }\n178 |       if (!inputs.targetTimeline) errors.targetTimeline = \"Please select a target timeline.\";\n179 |     } else if (gate === 3) {\n180 |       if (!inputs.preferredEngagementPath) errors.preferredEngagementPath = \"Please select an engagement pathway.\";\n181 |     }\n182 | \n183 |     setValidationErrors(errors);\n184 |     return Object.keys(errors).length === 0;\n185 |   };\n186 | \n187 |   const handleNextGate = () => {\n188 |     if (validateStep(activeStepGate)) {\n189 |       setActiveStepGate((prev) => (prev + 1) as 1 | 2 | 3);\n190 |     }\n191 |   };\n192 | \n193 |   const handleCompile = () => {\n194 |     if (!validateStep(3)) return;\n195 |     setStep(\"compiling\");\n196 |     setCompilingStepIndex(0);\n197 |   };\n198 | \n199 |   useEffect(() => {\n200 |     if (step !== \"compiling\") return;\n201 |     const interval = setInterval(() => {\n202 |       setCompilingStepIndex((prev) => {\n203 |         if (prev < compilingMessages.length - 1) return prev + 1;\n204 |         clearInterval(interval);\n205 |         setStep(\"preview\");\n206 |         return prev;\n207 |       });\n208 |     }, 450);\n209 |     return () => clearInterval(interval);\n210 |   }, [step]);\n211 | \n212 |   const handleSaveDraft = () => {\n213 |     if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n214 |       localStorage.setItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\", JSON.stringify(inputs));\n215 |       setSaved(true);\n216 |       setHasSavedDraft(true);\n217 |       setTimeout(() => setSaved(false), 2000);\n218 |     }\n219 |   };\n220 | \n221 |   const handleRestoreDraft = () => {\n222 |     if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n223 |       const draft = localStorage.getItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\");\n224 |       if (draft) {\n225 |         setInputs(JSON.parse(draft));\n226 |         setHasSavedDraft(false);\n227 |       }\n228 |     }\n229 |   };\n230 | \n231 |   const handleReset = () => {\n232 |     setInputs(INITIAL_INTAKE_INPUTS);\n233 |     setStep(\"configure\");\n234 |     setActiveStepGate(1);\n235 |     setIsSigned(false);\n236 |     setSignName(\"\");\n237 |     setSignTitle(\"\");\n238 |     setValidationErrors({});\n239 |     if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") {\n240 |       localStorage.removeItem(\"gff_proposal_draft_intake\");\n241 |       setHasSavedDraft(false);\n242 |     }\n243 |   };\n244 | \n245 |   const handlePrint = () => {\n246 |     if (typeof window !== \"undefined\") window.print();\n247 |   };\n248 | \n249 |   const handleCopyOutline = () => {\n250 |     const data = generateProposalData();\n251 |     const outlineText = `GFF AI SOVEREIGN INTEGRATION PROPOSAL\n252 | ----------------------------------------\n253 | Organization Name: ${data.org}\n254 | Sector Vertical: ${data.industryLabel}\n255 | Operational Footprint: ${data.companySizeLabel}\n256 | Geographic Deployment: ${data.geographyLabel}\n257 | Priority Challenge: ${data.challengeLabel}\n258 | Target Path: ${data.engagementPathObj.label} (${data.engagementPathObj.badge})\n259 | Project Scope Timeline: ${data.timelineLabel} (${data.weeks} Weeks)\n260 | Core Squad Config: ${data.engagementPathObj.squad}\n261 | Capital Allocation Range: ${data.budgetLabel}\n262 | Sponsor Stakeholders: ${data.stakeholdersLabel}\n263 | \n264 | KEY DELIVERABLES:\n265 | ${data.deliverables.map((d, i) => `${i + 1}. ${d}`).join(\"\\n\")}\n266 | `;\n267 |     navigator.clipboard.writeText(outlineText);\n268 |     setCopied(true);\n269 |     setTimeout(() => setCopied(false), 2000);\n270 |   };\n271 | \n272 |   const generateProposalData = () => {\n273 |     const org = inputs.companyName.trim() || \"Enterprise Client\";\n274 |     const indObj = INDUSTRIES.find((i) => i.id === inputs.industry) || INDUSTRIES[0];\n275 |     const sizeObj = COMPANY_SIZES.find((s) => s.id === inputs.companySize) || COMPANY_SIZES[2];\n276 |     const pathObj = ENGAGEMENT_PATHS.find((p) => p.id === inputs.preferredEngagementPath) || ENGAGEMENT_PATHS[1];\n277 |     const timelineObj = TIMELINES.find((t) => t.id === inputs.targetTimeline) || TIMELINES[1];\n278 |     const budgetObj = BUDGET_RANGES.find((b) => b.id === inputs.budgetRange) || BUDGET_RANGES[1];\n279 | \n280 |     const challengeLabel = inputs.primaryChallenge === \"other\" && inputs.customChallenge.trim()\n281 |       ? inputs.customChallenge.trim()\n282 |       : (CHALLENGES.find((c) => c.id === inputs.primaryChallenge)?.label || \"Sovereign Integration\");\n283 | \n284 |     const geographyLabel = inputs.geography.trim() || \"Global Private VPC Network Perimeter\";\n285 |     const stakeholdersLabel = inputs.stakeholders.trim() || \"Chief Technology Officer, Compliance Committee\";\n286 | \n287 |     const selectedOutcomeLabels = inputs.priorityOutcomes.map(\n288 |       (out) => OUTCOMES.find((o) => o.id === out)?.label || out\n289 |     );\n290 | \n291 |     let calculatedWeeks = timelineObj.weeks;\n292 |     if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"garage\") calculatedWeeks = 4;\n293 |     else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"operate\") calculatedWeeks = 52;\n294 |     else {\n295 |       if (inputs.companySize === \"small\") calculatedWeeks = Math.max(4, calculatedWeeks - 4);\n296 |       else if (inputs.companySize === \"global-conglomerate\") calculatedWeeks = calculatedWeeks + 4;\n297 |     }\n298 | \n299 |     const p1 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.15));\n300 |     const p2 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.30));\n301 |     const p3 = Math.max(1, Math.round(calculatedWeeks * 0.40));\n302 |     const p4 = Math.max(1, calculatedWeeks - (p1 + p2 + p3));\n303 | \n304 |     let deliverables: string[] = [];\n305 |     if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"garage\") {\n306 |       deliverables = [\n307 |         \"Interactive high-velocity client sandbox prototype\",\n308 |         \"Strategic SOW architecture topology outline schema\",\n309 |         \"Initial data pipeline schema risk audit assessment\",\n310 |         \"Targeted performance benchmarking telemetry sheet\"\n311 |       ];\n312 |     } else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"foundry\") {\n313 |       deliverables = [\n314 |         \"Fully provisioned, isolated single-tenant private VPC perimeter\",\n315 |         \"Tailored multi-agent consensus network and workflow configurations\",\n316 |         \"Hardened OmniMesh read-only legacy data connector pipelines\",\n317 |         \"Enterprise-wide compliance audit ledger logging software\"\n318 |       ];\n319 |     } else if (inputs.preferredEngagementPath === \"factory\") {\n320 |       deliverables = [\n321 |         \"Industrial-scale federated data mesh network connectors\",\n322 |         \"Autonomous auto-scaling cross-department agent fleet systems\",\n323 |         \"Highly integrated compliance watchdog and safety enforcer software\",\n324 |         \"Sovereign multi-region VPC peering configurations\"\n325 |       ];\n326 |     } else {\n327 |       deliverables = [\n328 |         \"Active monitoring uptime and model performance telemetry panels\",\n329 |         \"Guaranteed 99.9% operational performance SLA monitoring setup\",\n330 |         \"Proactive scheduled compliance and data policy updates\",\n331 |         \"Weekly technical optimization analysis reports and audit files\"\n332 |       ];\n333 |     }\n334 | \n335 |     return {\n336 |       org,\n337 |       industryLabel: indObj.label,\n338 |       industryDesc: indObj.desc,\n339 |       industryIcon: indObj.icon,\n340 |       companySizeLabel: sizeObj.label,\n341 |       companySizeDesc: sizeObj.desc,\n342 |       companySizeRange: sizeObj.range,\n343 |       challengeLabel,\n344 |       timelineLabel: timelineObj.label,\n345 |       weeks: calculatedWeeks,\n346 |       engagementPathObj: pathObj,\n347 |       budgetLabel: inputs.budgetRange ? budgetObj.label : \"Tailored Strategic Budget\",\n348 |       geographyLabel,\n349 |       stakeholdersLabel,\n350 |       selectedOutcomeLabels,\n351 |       deliverables,\n352 |       p1, p2, p3, p4\n353 |     };\n354 |   };\n355 | \n356 |   const pData = generateProposalData();\n357 | \n358 |   const renderTopologyDiagram = (path: \"garage\" | \"foundry\" | \"factory\" | \"operate\") => {\n359 |     return (\n360 |       <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl bg-[#030305] border border-white/5 font-mono text-[9px] text-white/50 space-y-3\">\n361 |         <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[7px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">\n362 |           <span>DEPLOYMENT TOPOLOGY MAP</span>\n363 |           <span className=\"text-[#00FF9D] font-bold\">{path.toUpperCase()}_ACTIVE_NODE</span>\n364 |         </div>\n365 |         <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-5 gap-2 items-center text-center\">\n366 |           <div className=\"p-2 border border-white/10 rounded bg-white/[0.01]\">📥 LOCAL INGEST</div>\n367 |           <div className=\"text-white/20 text-[8px] hidden sm:block\">────────▶</div>\n368 |           <div className=\"p-2.5 border border-[#009DFF]/30 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/5 font-bold text-white uppercase\">GFF_{path}</div>\n369 |           <div className=\"text-white/20 text-[8px] hidden sm:block\">────────▶</div>\n370 |           <div className=\"p-2 border border-[#00FF9D]/30 rounded bg-[#00FF9D]/5\">🛡️ SECURE ENCLAVE</div>\n371 |         </div>\n372 |         <p className=\"text-[8px] text-white/30 leading-snug\">\n373 |           <strong>COMPLIANCE SUMMARY:</strong> Workloads are fully orchestrated inside single-tenant enclaves inside the geographical boundary. Memory queues are cleared instantly post-token processing with absolute zero persistent retention pipelines.\n374 |         </p>\n375 |       </div>\n376 |     );\n377 |   };\n378 | \n379 |   if (!mounted) {\n380 |     return (\n381 |       <div className=\"min-h-screen bg-[#020204] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-mono text-xs\">\n382 |         Booting GFF Enterprise proposal workspace...\n383 |       </div>\n384 |     );\n385 |   }\n386 | \n387 |   return (\n388 |     <ToolPageShell showContact={step !== \"preview\"}>\n389 |       \n390 |       <ToolHero\n391 |         category=\"PHASE 3 // STRATEGIC ADVISORY SOW BUILDER\"\n392 |         title=\"Sovereign AI Proposal\"\n393 |         highlightedWord=\"Proposal\"\n394 |         description=\"Configure strategic integration models, design multi-agent topologies, and compile localized statement of work (SOW) blueprints completely offline.\"\n395 |       />\n396 | \n397 |       <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n398 |         \n399 |         {step === \"configure\" && (\n400 |           <motion.div\n401 |             key=\"configure\"\n402 |             initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12 }}\n403 |             animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}\n404 |             exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -12 }}\n405 |             className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\"\n406 |           >\n407 |             <div className=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-6\">\n408 |               {hasSavedDraft && (\n409 |                 <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#009DFF]/20 bg-[#009DFF]/5 flex items-center justify-between text-xs text-white animate-fadeIn\">\n410 |                   <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n411 |                     <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n412 |                     <span>In-progress draft detected from your previous workspace session.</span>\n413 |                   </div>\n414 |                   <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n415 |                     <button onClick={handleRestoreDraft} className=\"px-3 py-1.5 bg-[#009DFF]/20 border border-[#009DFF]/40 text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-mono hover:bg-[#009DFF]/40 transition uppercase font-bold rounded\">Restore Draft</button>\n416 |                     <button onClick={() => setHasSavedDraft(false)} className=\"px-2 py-1.5 text-white/40 text-[10px] font-mono hover:text-white uppercase\">Ignore</button>\n417 |                   </div>\n418 |                 </div>\n419 |               )}\n420 | \n421 |               {/* STEP TIMELINE GATE HEADER */}\n422 |               <div className=\"p-1 rounded-lg bg-black/45 border border-white/5 flex text-center text-[10px] font-mono\">\n423 |                 {[1, 2, 3].map((g) => (\n424 |                   <button\n425 |                     key={g}\n426 |                     type=\"button\"\n427 |                     onClick={() => { if (validateStep(1) && (g < 3 || validateStep(2))) setActiveStepGate(g as 1 | 2 | 3); }}\n428 |                     className={`flex-1 py-2 rounded transition font-semibold uppercase ${activeStepGate === g ? \"bg-white/5 text-[#009DFF] border border-white/10\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"}`}\n429 |                     disabled={g > activeStepGate && !validateStep(activeStepGate)}\n430 |                   >\n431 |                     0{g} {\"//\"} {g === 1 ? \"Baseline Profile\" : g === 2 ? \"Strategy & Outcomes\" : \"Deployment Pathway\"}\n432 |                   </button>\n433 |                 ))}\n434 |               </div>\n435 | \n436 |               {/* FORM WRAPPER CARD */}\n437 |               <div className=\"p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 relative overflow-hidden\">\n438 |                 <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-mono text-[8px] text-white/20\">\n439 |                   GFF_PROPOSAL_STUDIO // REV_2026\n440 |                 </div>\n441 | \n442 |                 {/* GATE 1: BASELINE */}\n443 |                 {activeStepGate === 1 && (\n444 |                   <div className=\"space-y-5 animate-fadeIn\">\n445 |                     <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n446 |                       <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">GATE 01 OF 03</span>\n447 |                       <h2 className=\"text-lg font-bold text-white mt-1\">Corporate Baseline Profile</h2>\n448 |                       <p className=\"text-white/40 text-[10px] font-light\">Specify your organization, vertical sector, operational scale, and target regional boundary constraints.</p>\n449 |                     </div>\n450 | \n451 |                     <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n452 |                       <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Organization Name (Optional)</label>\n453 |                       <input\n454 |                         type=\"text\"\n455 |                         value={inputs.companyName}\n456 |                         onChange={(e) => setInputs({ ...inputs, companyName: e.target.value })}\n457 |                         placeholder=\"e.g. Sovereign Global Mainframes\"\n458 |                         className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 h-11 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/20 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/60 transition\"\n459 |                       />\n460 |                     </div>\n461 | \n462 |                     <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n463 |                       <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n464 |                         <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Industry Vertical</label>\n465 |                         {validationErrors.industry && <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] font-bold\">{validationErrors.industry}</span>}\n466 |                       </div>\n467 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2.5\">\n468 |                         {INDUSTRIES.map((ind) => (\n469 |                           <button\n470 |                             key={ind.id}\n471 |                             type=\"button\"\n472 |                             onClick={() => { setInputs({ ...inputs, industry: ind.id }); setValidationErrors((prev) => ({ ...prev, industry: \"\" })); }}\n473 |                             className={`p-3 rounded-xl border text-left transition flex gap-3 items-start min-h-[60px] ${inputs.industry === ind.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(0,157,255,0.1)]\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-black/60\"}`}\n474 |                           >\n475 |                             <span className=\"text-base mt-0.5\">{ind.icon}</span>\n476 |                             <div>\n477 |                               <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-none\">{ind.label}</h4>\n478 |                               <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/40 leading-snug font-light mt-