=\"text-white/40\">SQUAD:</span> {path.squad}</div>\n652 |                               </div>\n653 |                             </button>\n654 |                           );\n655 |                         })}\n656 |                       </div>\n657 |                     </div>\n658 | \n659 |                     <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n660 |                       <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Capital Allocation Target (Optional)</label>\n661 |                       <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2.5\">\n662 |                         {BUDGET_RANGES.map((b) => (\n663 |                           <button\n664 |                             key={b.id}\n665 |                             type=\"button\"\n666 |                             onClick={() => setInputs({ ...inputs, budgetRange: b.id })}\n667 |                             className={`p-3 rounded-xl border text-left transition ${inputs.budgetRange === b.id ? \"border-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\" : \"border-white/5 bg-black/40 hover:border-white/10\"}`}\n668 |                           >\n669 |                             <h4 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{b.label}</h4>\n670 |                             <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 leading-tight mt-1 font-light\">{b.desc}</p>\n671 |                           </button>\n672 |                         ))}\n673 |                       </div>\n674 |                     </div>\n675 | \n676 |                     <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n677 |                       <label className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wide block\">Sponsor Stakeholders (Optional)</label>\n678 |                       <input\n679 |                         type=\"text\"\n680 |                         value={inputs.stakeholders}\n681 |                         onChange={(e) => setInputs({ ...inputs, stakeholders: e.target.value })}\n682 |                         placeholder=\"e.g. VP of Security, Lead Compliance Architect\"\n683 |                         className=\"w-full bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 h-11 text-xs text-white placeholder-white/25 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF] transition\"\n684 |                       />\n685 |                     </div>\n686 |                   </div>\n687 |                 )}\n688 | \n689 |                 {/* BOTTOM STEPS BUTTONS */}\n690 |                 <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-5 mt-6 flex justify-between items-center\">\n691 |                   <button\n692 |                     type=\"button\"\n693 |                     onClick={() => setActiveStepGate((prev) => (prev - 1) as 1 | 2 | 3)}\n694 |                     disabled={activeStepGate === 1}\n695 |                     className={`px-4 h-9 rounded-lg border text-xs font-mono uppercase transition ${activeStepGate === 1 ? \"border-white/5 text-white/10 cursor-not-allowed\" : \"border-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/5\"}`}\n696 |                   >\n697 |                     Back\n698 |                   </button>\n699 |                   <div className=\"flex gap-2.5\">\n700 |                     <button\n701 |                       type=\"button\"\n702 |                       onClick={handleSaveDraft}\n703 |                       className=\"px-3.5 h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-xs font-mono text-white hover:bg-white/5 transition uppercase\"\n704 |                     >\n705 |                       {saved ? \"✓ Saved\" : \"[ Save Draft ]\"}\n706 |                     </button>\n707 |                     {activeStepGate < 3 ? (\n708 |                       <button\n709 |                         type=\"button\"\n710 |                         onClick={handleNextGate}\n711 |                         className=\"px-4 h-9 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#009DFF] text-black hover:bg-[#009DFF]/90 font-mono\"\n712 |                       >\n713 |                         Next Gate\n714 |                       </button>\n715 |                     ) : (\n716 |                       <button\n717 |                         type=\"button\"\n718 |                         onClick={handleCompile}\n719 |                         className=\"px-4 h-9 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold uppercase bg-[#00FF9D] text-black hover:bg-[#00FF9D]/90 font-mono\"\n720 |                       >\n721 |                         Compile SOW Blueprint\n722 |                       </button>\n723 |                     )}\n724 |                   </div>\n725 |                 </div>\n726 |               </div>\n727 |             </div>\n728 |             \n729 |             <div className=\"lg:col-span-4 lg:sticky lg:top-8 space-y-4 hidden lg:block\">\n730 |               <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030306]/95 text-left relative animate-fadeIn\">\n731 |                 {/* Telemetry flashing dot */}\n732 |                 <div className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n733 |                   <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9D] animate-ping\" />\n734 |                   <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">LIVE COMPILING</span>\n735 |                 </div>\n736 | \n737 |                 <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/35 font-bold uppercase block mb-3\">SOW compilation blueprint</span>\n738 | \n739 |                 <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n740 |                   {/* Entity Metadata */}\n741 |                   <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-lg bg-black/60 border border-white/5 font-mono text-[9.5px] leading-relaxed space-y-1.5 text-white/60\">\n742 |                     <div>\n743 |                       <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">ENTITY:</span>{\" \"}\n744 |                       <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{pData.org}</span>\n745 |                     </div>\n746 |                     <div>\n747 |                       <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase\">VERTICAL:</span>{\" \"}\n748 |                       <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-semibold\">{pData.industryLabel}</span>\n749 |                     </div>\n750 |                     <div>","success":true}],"durationMs":3}}
